{"tid":864442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(事先張揚) 港鐵分階段更換7條市區綫信號系統　料2026年完成","createTime":"2018-10-16T08:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T08:25:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94dbd30c54b01e5198bb64e11eda9f093a39e9ea","tid":864442,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"港鐵投資33億元，分階段更換7條市區綫的信號系統。荃灣綫是首條換系統的路綫，港鐵說工程進度已達到7成，已安裝超過200個信號發射器，有一半列車加裝了新設備，餘下3成工作主要是測試，包括與控制中心協調，停站位置是否準確等。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵說，測試人員午夜收車後，會切換至新系統進行測試，翌日早上再轉回現有系統以提供服務。若轉換系統過程如果不暢順，列車服務或會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵又說現時荃灣綫的測試規模逐步擴大，利用多架列車在全綫不同範圍測試，已進入風險較高的測試階段，但強調已制定應變措施，例如安排工程人員、車站人手及免費接駁巴士候命，呼籲市民出門前留意車務狀況。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵預料2026年各條市區綫更換好信號系統後，整體載客能力可提升一成。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1364842-20171115.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1364842-20171115.htm&d=4ca4e27lY2GGV30PmgtKiI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9cb13d79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1364842-20171115.htm&h=47e170cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1364842-20171115.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3346e8a5a971a78dd0f069993bce39a3953eb98e","tid":864442,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"壞到2026<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b38011559c1ddae609a9cd6fb1d53e936f6a5fe","tid":864442,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3346e8a5a971a78dd0f069993bce39a3953eb98e","tid":864442,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"壞到2026<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"到時打緊WW3了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f5d978a31e7490d4ed6fbc5ac86619c7dcda88","tid":864442,"uid":155137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"要2026先有勤工獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}